{"arkId":"cl010099972","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010099972","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Montre ronde","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Montre ronde"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Louis XIV (1643-1715) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1650 - 1675","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 531 - Paul Garnier, Vitrine 1","room":"Salle 531, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1650,"endYear":1675,"imprecision":"","text":"3e quart du XVIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Rousseau, David","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"1641","place":"","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1738","place":"","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Horloger","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 8445","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"horlogerie ; montre","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Fond d\u00e9cor\u00e9 d\u0027une sc\u00e8ne figurant V\u00e9nus et Adonis assis sous tente dress\u00e9e dans un paysage. Contre-\u00e9mail peint d\u0027un paysage repr\u00e9sentant un coin de village pr\u00e8s d\u0027une rivi\u00e8re. Carrure orn\u00e9e de quatre m\u00e9daillons contenant des paysages vari\u00e9s s\u00e9par\u00e9s par des fleurons blancs sur fond noir. Lunette du verre grav\u00e9e de stries formant des coeurs. Charni\u00e8re sous le pendant qui est en forme de boule. Cadran \u00e0 chiffres romains, au centre est peint un couple d\u0027amoureux, sans doute V\u00e9nus et Adonis. Fausse plaque grav\u00e9e sur son pourtour. Platine du mouvement d\u00e9cor\u00e9e d\u0027une plaque reperc\u00e9e et cisel\u00e9e de rinceaux. Echappement \u00e0 roue de rencontre, fus\u00e9e avec cha\u00eenette, vis-sans-fin. Quatre piliers reperc\u00e9s et cisel\u00e9s de rinceaux. Coq \u00e0 un pied allong\u00e9 grav\u00e9 et reperc\u00e9 prot\u00e9geant le balancier r\u00e9gl\u00e9 par un spiral.","inscriptions":"Poin\u00e7on : \r ; petite garantie, Paris, depuis 1838 (deux fois) ; importation, France, 1838-1864 \r ; Signature : \r ; mouvement sign\u00e9 : David\/Rousseau","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"5,2","displayDimension":"5,2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"3,7","displayDimension":"3,7 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"3,4","displayDimension":"3,4 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"1,7","displayDimension":"1,7 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":4,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : or\r\nMat\u00e9riau : argent\r\nMat\u00e9riau : laiton\r\nTechnique : dor\u00e9 = dorure (techniques m\u00e9tal)\r\nTechnique : \u00e9maill\u00e9 = \u00e9maillage = \u00e9mail = \u00e9maux (techniques m\u00e9tal)\r\nTechnique : techniques m\u00e9tal (orf\u00e8vrerie)","placeOfCreation":"Gen\u00e8ve (Europe-\u003ESuisse)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"collection Jules-Ren\u00e9 Olivier (1855-1933), horloger-collectionneur ; legs de sa s\u0153ur Marie-Julie Olivier, n\u00b0 642 ; comit\u00e9 du 24 janvier 1935 ; conseil du 5 f\u00e9vrier 1935 ; d\u00e9cret du 4 ao\u00fbt 1935 ; d\u00e9pos\u00e9e au mus\u00e9e des Arts d\u00e9coratifs le 4 novembre 1935 ; retour au mus\u00e9e 